@startuml
actor 用户 as User

'
' Use Cases
'
usecase "启动图形编辑器" as UC1
usecase "创建图形" as UC2
usecase "选择图形" as UC3
usecase "删除图形" as UC4
usecase "调整图形尺寸" as UC5
usecase "移动图形" as UC6
usecase "创建新图层" as UC7
usecase "管理图层" as UC8

'
' Associations
'
User --> UC1
User --> UC2
User --> UC3
User --> UC4
User --> UC5
User --> UC6
User --> UC7
User --> UC8

'
' Include relationships (with causal comments)
'
' 删除图形必须先选择图形
UC4 ..> UC3 : <<include>>
' 调整图形尺寸必须先选择图形
UC5 ..> UC3 : <<include>>
' 移动图形必须先选择图形
UC6 ..> UC3 : <<include>>

'
' Extend relationships (with conditions in comments)
'
' 创建新图层在图层数量未超过16个时才可执行，否则无法创建（扩展点：图层数量检查）
' Note: extend forbidden by constraint, so not added
'
' 管理图层中的“下一页”操作可触发图层切换（但切换本身不是独立用例）
' Note: "切换图层" is forbidden, so no such use case exists

@enduml
